The '''King''' or '''Queen of the Phosphura Belt Pirates''', also known as the '''Pirate King''', was the highest ranking leader of the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]]. Pirate Queens and Kings were assisted by [[Buccaneer]]s. The first Pirate King was [[Arvo Norstrag]]. In the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], their king was [[Leo Bellsfar/Legends|Leo Bellsfar]].

